{"data":[{"date":"10:58 25/07","title":"T\u1edbi Juve, Emre Can tri \u00e2n th\u1ea7y c\u0169","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/1/16/toi-juve-emre-can-tri-an-thay-cu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n sang Serie A t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Klopp<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 4 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i cho Juventus mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. \u0110\u1ec3 n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ra \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p, Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Jurgen Klopp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Klopp lu\u00f4n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00fac t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi t\u00f4i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1eddi Liverpool trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n Emre Can c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i. Nh\u01b0ng &ldquo;b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i&rdquo;, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Cris Ronaldo. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Ronaldo. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juve, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp\" title=\"Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juve, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i xem nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng chung chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, d\u00f9 c\u00e1c CLB Italia kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2u. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Turin, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0o d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a CLB.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Champions League. Juve \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, v\u00e0 n\u0103m nay c\u0169ng \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Fabinho &ndash; Keita.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua-172-191977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua-172-191977.html\">Mourinho: Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n MU \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/khong-du-dau-cung-juventus-cristiano-ronaldo-sang-trung-quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-176-191950.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/khong-du-dau-cung-juventus-cristiano-ronaldo-sang-trung-quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-176-191950.html\">Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus, Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u00f9ng Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mang t\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4606","checkdouble":"191975"},{"date":"09:44 25/07","title":"Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Bordeaux v\u00ec l\u1eadt k\u00e8o v\u1ee5 Malcom","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/roma-chuan-bi-khoi-kien-bordeaux-vi-lat-keo-vu-malcom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n sao tr\u1ebb Malcom r\u1ed3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb Barca \u201cv\u1ed3\u201d m\u1ea5t, CLB AS Roma kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Bordeaux v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef ch\u1eef t\u00edn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 l\u00e0m \u0103n n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRoma \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil &ndash; Malcom b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh ti\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Everton \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Premier League. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ngay sau khi Roma c\u00f3 kinh ph\u00ed (sau khi b\u00e1n Alisson), ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh quay ngo\u1eaft v\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 &ldquo;Malcom mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Italia&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 ngay khi c\u1ea3 Roma l\u1eabn Bordeaux \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, b\u1ea5t th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh Barca nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 Malcom m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u1eadt m\u1eb7t. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Cam Nou v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 41 tri\u1ec7u euro &ndash; nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Everton hay Roma \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, G\u0110TT Monchi c\u1ee7a CLB Italia \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t th\u00f3i l\u1eadt m\u1eb7t tr\u01a1 tr\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Bordeaux v\u00e0 \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n. &ldquo;Ph\u00f9 th\u1ee7y chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t th\u1ef1c thi nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ph\u00e1p l\u00fd. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Malcom v\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bordeaux (Stephane Martin) \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AS Roma kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Bordeaux sau khi b\u1ecb l\u1eadt k\u00e8o v\u1ee5 Malcom\" title=\"Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AS Roma kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Bordeaux sau khi b\u1ecb l\u1eadt k\u00e8o v\u1ee5 Malcom</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Martin \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Barca, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ua gi\u00e1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u00e1p l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 &ndash; v\u00e0 ng\u00e0i Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Bordeaux kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o ch\u1ee9ng minh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mi\u1ec7ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roma, \u00f4ng James Pallotta r\u1eb1ng ph\u00eda Bordeaux \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadt m\u1eb7t. Pallotta b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u01a1n. Sau c\u00f9ng, t\u00f4i b\u1ea3o nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tham gia v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i&rdquo; &ndash; Monchi gi\u1eadn d\u1eef cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ecb l\u1eadt m\u1eaft tr\u00e1o tr\u1edf b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng CLB AS Roma kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Bordeaux th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Malcom, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ra m\u1eaft Barca v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c h\u00f4n l\u00ean logo CLB n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 trung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-phat-bieu-sau-khi-gia-nhap-barca-180-191961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/liverpool-sap-tai-hop-cap-bai-trung-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-phat-bieu-sau-khi-gia-nhap-barca-180-191961.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Brazil n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1edbi Barca th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt?</span><br>\r\nMalcom ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c sau AS Roma nh\u01b0ng Barcelona l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4605","checkdouble":"191956"},{"date":"09:03 25/07","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb Brazil n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1edbi Barca th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/liverpool-sap-tai-hop-cap-bai-trung-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Malcom ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Malcom</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, AS Roma m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Malcom. \u0110\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Bordeaux c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng, Barcelona &ldquo;c\u01b0\u1edbp&rdquo; th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNghe \u0111\u00e2u, ph\u00eda Roma c\u00f2n \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec7n Barca l\u00ean t\u00f2a \u00e1n th\u1ec3 thao. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n song v\u1eabn tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Malcom ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Malcom ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/liverpool-sap-tai-hop-cap-bai-trung-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Malcom chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barca t\u1eeb Bordeaux</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Malcom l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMalcom sinh ng\u00e0y 26 th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m 1997 t\u1ea1i Sao Paulo, Brazil. Anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bordeaux n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. 2 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean U23 Brazil t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 m\u00f9a 2017/18 ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, Malcom ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ed9ng 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, gi\u00fap Bordeaux c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch Ligue \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c t\u1edbi Barca gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i th\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Malcom gia nhap Barca\" title=\"Malcom gia nhap Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Malcom-gia-nhap-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Malcom ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca v\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. \u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt</em>&rdquo;, Malcom ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi gia nh\u1eadp Barca. &ldquo;<em>T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mong \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u00e0 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 vui m\u1eebng v\u00e0 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u1ea5p \u1ee7 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n b\u00e9</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-willian-toi-barca-172-191930.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-191898.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-len-duong-sang-my-messi-vang-mat-180-191877.html\">Barca l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang M\u1ef9, Messi v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca-180-191808.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Barca th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 Messi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4604","checkdouble":"191961"},{"date":"09:04 25/07","title":"Real Madrid ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua sao tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/real-chot-gia-mua-lloris.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thay m\u00e1u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</h2><h2>CLB&nbsp;Real h\u1ecfi mua th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/real-chot-gia-mua-lloris.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Hugo Lloris (tr\u00e1i) l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Real l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Real trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 qua nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Keylor Navas ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng tin tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> th\u00e0nh Madrid. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Navas \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda khi Los Blancos \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 l\u00ean th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN h\u1ecfi mua nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, Hugo Lloris.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd The Sun, Real \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a CLB Tottenham m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh (79 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4-la).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Real d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 nh\u01b0 David de Gea v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Lloris \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia l\u1ea1i khao kh\u00e1t s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lloris t\u1eeb Tottenham b\u1edfi anh \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Spurs c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2022.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina-421-191641.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-truong-phap-tiet-lo-dieu-dac-biet-sau-chien-thang-truoc-argentina-421-191641.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</span><br>\r\nHugo Lloris ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-duc-danh-gia-nhung-thu-mon-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-191389.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/huyen-thoai-duc-danh-gia-nhung-thu-mon-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-duc-danh-gia-nhung-thu-mon-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018-421-191389.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Oliver Kahn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Hugo Lloris, Thibaut Courtois, Danijel Subasic v\u00e0 Jordan Pickford sau m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4603","checkdouble":"191965"},{"date":"09:22 25/07","title":"Thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/dembele-muon-chay-tron-khoi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Nou Camp, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Ousmane Dembele d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay Barca trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Thi-dau-te-hai,-tien-dao-Ousmane-Dembele-muon-ra-di-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean t\u1ea1i Barca</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ousmane Dembele gia nh\u1eadp Barca \u1edf nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c. Anh l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Barca t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 145 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed (sau Neymar).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, &ldquo;si\u00eau bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; m\u00e0 Barca mua v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. Sau khi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 23 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, k\u00e9m xa so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi anh c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, Dembele l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca. V\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2n binh Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux, nguy c\u01a1 Dembele ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay Barca. Theo \u0111\u00e0i Cadena Cope, Dembele \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean HLV&nbsp;Ernesto Valverde l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-willian-toi-barca-172-191930.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-willian-toi-barca.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-neu-willian-toi-barca-172-191930.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Willian t\u1edbi Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-191898.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/5/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-willian-cho-barca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-willian-cho-barca-172-191898.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool-180-191758.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/20/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool-180-191758.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\nSimon Mignolet t\u1edbi Barca l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u1ebfu Jasper Cillessen ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4602","checkdouble":"191966"},{"date":"09:18 25/07","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u1ee7ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/28/them-mot-tien-dao-khung-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Edinson Cavani, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda PSG y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Los Blancos \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real kh\u00e1t khao m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong hai k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i h\u1ecd b\u00e1n Alvaro Morata cho Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 cho Bayern Munich m\u01b0\u1ee3n James Rodriguez 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Edinson Cavani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Edinson Cavani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Edinson-Cavani-voi-gia-53-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111ang t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Ronaldo&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 2018, Real \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, James Rodriguez tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Bayern. Vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u bu\u1ed9c Los Blancos ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song PSG l\u1ea1i h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao. K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi 400 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Neymar v\u00e0 290 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Mbappe.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Real quan t\u00e2m Eden Hazard</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi Chelsea \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Edinson Cavani, Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda PSG y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Los Blancos \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Edinson Cavani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Edinson Cavani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Edinson-Cavani-voi-gia-53-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real nh\u1eafm Edinson Cavani n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Cavani l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao Neymar, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f2n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn\" title=\"bong da\" type=\"bong da\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span> n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u00e1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1987.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111\u00f2i 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Cavani v\u00e0 Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00e0y thay th\u1ebf c\u1ef1u sao Napoli. Morata \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i song Cavani v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. \u1ede World Cup 2018 anh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Uruguay. Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung phong t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4601","checkdouble":"191967"},{"date":"11:32 25/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 25/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-2507.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 25/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2507 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2507 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2507-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Malcom ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c sau AS Roma nh\u01b0ng Barcelona l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Barca ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ousmane Dembele mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Malcom, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, hi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Coutinho th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec Barca kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho se rat vui neu Willian toi Barca\" title=\"Coutinho s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Willian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Willian, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30. Theo Sport, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Coutinho t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Willian \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Tottenham v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail, v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y Tottenham s\u1ebd cho ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh Andre Gomes t\u1eeb Barca, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Inter v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec Aleix Vidal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Inter Milan v\u00e0 Roma l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Aleix Vidal c\u1ee7a Barca, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Everton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina quyet o lai Barca\" title=\"Mina quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/nguoi-hung-colombia-quyet-tam-bam-tru-tai-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport, Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8.\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Messi v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Marcos Alonso</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport, Messi v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Marcos Alonso c\u1ee7a Chelsea. M10 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Jasper Cillessen</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Theo Goal, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4600","checkdouble":"191981"},{"date":"09:44 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City 07h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-liverpool-vs-man-city-07h00-ngay-267-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool vs Man City l\u00fac 07h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City 07h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool vs Man City 07h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Liverpool-vs-Manchester-City.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool vs Manchester City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>\u00a0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Liverpool vs Man City: 3-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y Man City \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 16 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh n\u00e0o c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga nh\u01b0 Man xanh. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5.636 ph\u00fat \u1edf World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t CLB thu\u1ed9c Premier League \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 2018. N\u00f3i v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn Pep ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u. Vi\u1ec7c Man City g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Pep kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i v\u00e1 v\u00edu Man xanh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Dortmund tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 l\u00e0 Claudio Bravo, Oleksandr Zinchenko v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Riyad Mahrez. N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh chi ly h\u01a1n, c\u1ea3 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Man xanh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ai th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSang hi\u1ec7p 2, Pep c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra 7 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Leroy Sane l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t quen thu\u1ed9c. T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, Man City hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 Raheem Sterling, Gabriel Jesus, David Silva, De Bruyne, Fernandinho\u2026 S\u00e1ng mai, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Man City g\u1ed3m h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pep s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. N\u1ebfu v\u1eady, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 Man xanh v\u1eeba th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Dortmund v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00f3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb World Cup 2018 t\u00e0n ph\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 Man City. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, HLV Juergen Klopp l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong tay h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1eeb tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man xanh. Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 Naby Keita, Fabinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ra m\u1eaft. V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf ICC 2018, Liverpool r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Man City r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c th\u00ec The Kop c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Klopp \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong TTCN m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Man City. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu Man xanh coi ICC l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c d\u1ea1o ch\u01a1i th\u00ec Liverpool coi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n th\u1eed l\u1eeda th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Klopp hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng sau nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i mang v\u1ec1 Anfield m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u. S\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u1ec1 danh hi\u1ec7u s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Klopp kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean Liverpool ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Man City. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Gegenpressing r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man xanh \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin<br>\r\nLiverpool th\u1eafng 8, thua 12/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n14/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung.<br>\r\n13/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. <br>\r\nMan City th\u1eafng 9, thua 8/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 b\u00e0n hi\u1ec7p 1<br>\r\n16/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 1. 14/20 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. NHM n\u00ean \u0111\u1ee3i sau 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng hi\u1ec7p 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi c\u01a1 cho Aymeric Laporte<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 ba trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00e0 John Stones, Nicolas Otamendi v\u00e0 Vincent Kompany \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9 v\u00ec v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 Laporte th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eb1m chi\u1ebfm v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Laporte \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Dortmund v\u00ec m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Liverpool. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPH\u00c1T BI\u1ec2U<br>\r\n\u201cLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 thua Dortmund v\u00ec c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Liverpool s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d. <br>\r\nHLV Juergen Klopp (Liverpool)<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Th\u1eafng thua \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d. HLV Pep Guardiola (Man City)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u1ee1 \u201cthi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i\u201d v\u00ec World Cup 2018 h\u01a1n Man City<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y Liverpool ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 The Kop c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 3.433 ph\u00fat \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, so v\u1edbi 5.636 ph\u00fat c\u1ee7a Man City. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Liverpool \u0111\u1ee1 \u201cthi\u1ec7t h\u1ea1i\u201d v\u00ec World Cup 2018 h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Man xanh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4599","checkdouble":"191973"},{"date":"10:29 25/07","title":"Everton ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Premier League 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRicharlison t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p th\u1ea7y c\u0169<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Everton \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Marco Silva \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi l\u00f4i k\u00e9o c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Richarlison t\u1eeb CLB Watford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Silva \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 11,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1eeb CLB Brazil Fluminense. Ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 5 n\u0103m c\u00f9ng l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi mua 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed khi\u1ebfn Everton ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p th\u1ea7y c\u0169, bom t\u1ea5n Richarlison cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Marco Silva. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea1i Watford, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhau. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea1y t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Brazil. Marco Silva c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cEverton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00f4i v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n vinh danh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi tri \u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, HLV Marco Silva c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap CLB c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Brazil r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed sau l\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span><br>\r\nEverton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh dung c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham-172-191673.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham-172-191673.html\">Sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh NHA b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham</span><br>\r\nZaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tin vui cho m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4598","checkdouble":"191974"},{"date":"10:53 25/07","title":"Mourinho: \"Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n MU \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mat-7-cau-thu-quan-trong-mu-se-da-the-nao-o-vong-mo-man-nha-mua-toi-172-191532.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U s\u1ebd v\u1eafng t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA 2018/19</span> g\u1eb7p Leicester. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Paul Pogba, Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford, Jesse Lingard, Marouane Fellaini, Ashley Young v\u00e0 Phil Jones s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-MU-truoc-viec-mat-7-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U v\u1eafng 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 55 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u0103m nay b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10/08.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng MU b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho rat muon tai hop voi Willian o MU\" title=\"Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. M.U, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi v\u1eafng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i nh\u00ecn sang Leicester, n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng sai, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Jamie Vardy v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o Brighton, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o v\u00ec World Cup. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u00e2y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0 Brighton v\u1edbi M.U kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4597","checkdouble":"191977"},{"date":"11:20 25/07","title":"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/cuc-nong-chelsea-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-38-tuoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robert Green, The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, theo \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 38 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Robert Green</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robert Green. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robert Green h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robert Green h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/cuc-nong-chelsea-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-38-tuoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Robert Green</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e1ng 8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Green k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Huddersfield, song d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi David Wagner anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 38 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Huddersfield \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2018, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian t\u00ednh to\u00e1n anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London the d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Robert Green.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i, Chelsea s\u1ebd t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Pepe Reina. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Robert Green cho th\u1ea5y The Blues s\u1eafp chia tay Thibaut Courtois ho\u1eb7c Willy Caballero.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGreen \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 658 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong 19 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 12 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Theo Mirror, Robert Green \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 thay Caballero, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Robert Green v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. HLV Sarri x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Chelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"sarri\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Chu-tich-Napoli-chi-trich-HLV-Sarri-phu-bac-voi-doi-bong-cu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng 2 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa m\u1edbi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Chelsea quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 151 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 ba Higuain, Rugani v\u00e0 Pjanic c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-morata-neu-roi-chelsea-172-191433.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Morata cho AC Milan</span>, David Luiz v\u00e0 Gary Cahill c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4596","checkdouble":"191978"},{"date":"11:22 25/07","title":"G\u00f3c Liverpool: Qua r\u1ed3i th\u1eddi d\u00f9ng dao \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/goc-liverpool-qua-roi-thoi-dung-dao-dau-voi-cac-xa-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d m\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mua s\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mo Salah t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00f9ng Merseyside trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec ph\u1ebf tru\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng &ldquo;bom x\u1ecbt&rdquo; Andy Carroll (gia nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i). H\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m sau, c\u00f3 ai ng\u1edd <u>Salah t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 5 trong danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool</u> cao gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Qua r\u1ed3i th\u1eddi d\u00f9ng dao \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Qua r\u1ed3i th\u1eddi d\u00f9ng dao \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/11/Chuyen-nhuong-Liverpool-Qua-roi-thoi-dung-dao-dau-voi-cac-xa-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Naby Keita (53,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Fabinho (40 tri\u1ec7u), Xherdan Shaqiri (13,1 tri\u1ec7u) v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Alisson (55,7) n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, n\u1ebfu Liverpool kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Nabil Fekir, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 th\u00eam &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; c\u00f2n Salah xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, <strong>suy ngh\u0129 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i</strong>. M\u1ed9t Salah tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u1edd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Robbie-Fowler-phat-bieu-ve-Alisson-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alisson g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i Salah</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn c\u0169ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n</em>. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u00ecn nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. C\u00f2n gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i kim ti\u1ec1n, gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u0103ng l\u00ean phi m\u00e3. G\u1ea7n 2 th\u00e1ng sau khi Liverpool ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng CLB v\u1edbi Salah, PSG ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i: 197 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mang v\u1ec1 Neymar t\u1eeb Barcelona. Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi &ldquo;bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t&rdquo; t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp theo \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <em>th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng d\u00f9 l\u1edbn hay nh\u1ecf, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 thu\u1eadn</em>. The Kop ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e2u ra ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00e2y t\u00f2 m\u00f2 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1eb1ng <strong>th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n</strong>. V\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Virgil van Dijk, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. V\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ph\u00e1 s\u00e2u k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Alisson, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1edbn h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" title=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Alisson-Fabinho-Keita.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng &quot;bom t\u1ea5n&quot; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 Klopp, ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft khai th\u00e1c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Roberto Firmino l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brendan Rodgers \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFirmino c\u00f9ng Salah v\u00e0 Sadio Mane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng <em>t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng</em> h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Keita, Fabinho hay Alisson. B\u1ed9 ba MFS c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Shaqiri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i Premier League c\u00f9ng Stoke v\u00e0 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge can thiet cho Liverpool\" title=\"Sturridge can thiet cho Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-can-thiet-cho-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</strong> thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Rafa Benitez, C\u0110V c\u1ee7a The Kop m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0 Man City, Man United, Chelsea hay Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Van Dijk, Fabinho, Alisson hay Shaqiri trong 1 n\u0103m qua. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh sau 28 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp tu tin gianh danh hieu cung Liverpool\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/klopp-nam-nay-se-la-nam-cua-chung-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng 15 n\u0103m qua, Liverpool t\u1ecf ra l\u00e9p v\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Alex Ferguson r\u1ed3i Chelsea, Man City v\u1edbi t\u00fai ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1y. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, M.U \u0111\u00e3 suy y\u1ebfu th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Sir Alex trong khi Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, Man City m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y <u>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</u>. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mang dao \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7. C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-sturridge-o-lai-liverpool-la-dieu-tot-cho-tat-ca-172-191904.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-sau-khi-liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-becker-172-191685.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau khi Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-thu-mon-alisson-dau-roi-loi-mia-mai-172-191662.html\">Liverpool bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-becker-giai-ma-tan-binh-liverpool-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191660.html\">Alisson Becker: Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool &ndash; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-ho-da-co-de-gea-cua-rieng-minh-172-191659.html\">Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson: H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4595","checkdouble":"191980"},{"date":"07:01 25/07","title":"Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus, Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/6.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u00f9ng Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mang t\u00ean CR7.\r\n\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Cristiano-Ronaldo-sang-Trung-Quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gay chu y khi luon duoc mot ve si luc luong theo sat nhu hinh voi bong.\" title=\"Ronaldo g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ec7 s\u0129 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo s\u00e1t nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ec7 s\u0129 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo s\u00e1t nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo sang Trung Quoc de quang ba cho Nike cung nhu thuong hieu CR7 cua ban than. Nike coi Trung Quoc la thi truong trong diem, trong khi Adidas dat trong tam thi truong o Nhat Ban.\" title=\"Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u CR7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Nike coi Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Adidas \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/065845-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u CR7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Nike coi Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Adidas \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n  